{"tid":5840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行山小毒","createTime":"2016-11-27T05:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T18:21:16.000Z","uid":25280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81ee34731111a903f00d884f3a06265ad2a8762a","tid":5840,"uid":25280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:41:24.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲平時有冇行下山咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想知有咩山係比較易行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為有朋友身形問題落山容易上山難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黎緊17號可能會行，但就未定行咩山，希望行程會係4到6個鐘（由上山開始計到落山）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842848548790074e59d5493a8e54a4f2f917e36b","tid":5840,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"肥得滯碌落山？"},{"pid":"752f8429f03172555c8b679f490f5ff2dcfacaa9","tid":5840,"uid":21790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"菠蘿山囉 夠易行 回慢慢行4個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e48120b0ef6bc98a01aff2fd2d0eb787fe1ed3a","tid":5840,"uid":3037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥得滯碌落山？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f8ee2426172cb789f87749c481d29ee2da1283","tid":5840,"uid":25280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菠蘿山囉 夠易行 回慢慢行4個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前兩個星期行完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96963a9b8227759c5309ec0cd28c9f98df6d66fb","tid":5840,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:08:54.000Z","msg":"荔枝窩"},{"pid":"c2f463346c79f82881c75d4ac641fadf4197e8e4","tid":5840,"uid":25280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥得滯碌落山？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔係咁既程度"},{"pid":"b75c354c5ca154487f51a34a45819d9c4a24d902","tid":5840,"uid":25280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>荔枝窩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似幾正喎<br />\n<br />\n利申未行過呢到"},{"pid":"fc714e5798b83e4c4ac2dca6cf2095ad5ace2f32","tid":5840,"uid":17268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"咁你本身行過d 咩路線"},{"pid":"09621312e50984b91e74cddfbe3bd25784499057","tid":5840,"uid":25280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你本身行過d 咩路線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最難既行過黃牛山、水牛山落第一城，最易既行過培門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712c546d2c1420c9ea917fb01e6ceae0e5b4b0b4","tid":5840,"uid":25280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁你本身行過d 咩路線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最難既行過黃牛山、水牛山落第一城，最易既行過塔門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b536efef7f4346f772db1d67d48bc41c46a9a80b","tid":5840,"uid":21611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:10:49.000Z","msg":"草山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65cdd3531021b83ce253025c380f2dccf1d2ca7c","tid":5840,"uid":38580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:21:16.000Z","msg":"城門水塘 超易行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}